Enable Annotations on Dashboard Widgets

REQUIRED EDITIONS: Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To enable annotations, complete the following steps:

From Setup, enter Feed Tracking in the Quick Find box, and then select Feed Tracking under Chatter.
Scroll down and select Analytics Asset.
Select Enable Feed Tracking.
Click Save.
Collaborate with Dashboard Annotations
title: Enabling Annotations on CRM Analytics Dashboards
